Description: Produces an economic evaluation of a Bayesian model in the form of MCMC simulations.
             Given suitable variables of cost and effectiveness / utility for two or more interventions,
             this package computes the most cost-effective alternative and produces graphical summaries and probabilistic sensitivity analysis.
